00:29:34.820 --> 00:29:38.600
And little did I know that
what I was doing at that point

00:29:38.600 --> 00:29:42.470
was kind of calming
down my neocortex.

00:29:42.470 --> 00:29:46.220
I was staying in that little
sliver of reasonableness

00:29:46.220 --> 00:29:49.400
while the kind of flood of
the whole rest of my brain

00:29:49.400 --> 00:29:52.280
was taking over and acting like
it was some kind of emergency.

00:29:52.280 --> 00:29:52.910
SPEAKER 1: Yes.

